The teaching practice lasts 10 weeks. The students will visit, analyse and give lessons in basic school (20 lessons) and in gymnasium (20 lessons).Objectives/eesmärkid:  Pedagogical practice gives an overview about general principles of education at school, about the role of language teacher in learning proces. Students learn to analyse teaching and learning proces. They will visit, analyse and give lessons in basic school (20 lessons) and in gymnasium (20 lessons).Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  After completing the practice students:
- are able to conduct lessons in language and literature subject;
- are able to formulate aims for lessons, plan and analyse the learning and teaching process.
